‚≠ê When Windows Search is okay:

Use Windows Search only if:

You have few PDFs

No complex layouts

Windows indexing is working
But it often misses results.

‚≠ê When Python script is useful:

Use Python only if:

You need to automate search regularly

You must extract data

You want a custom tool
But it requires installing libraries and is slower with large PDFs.

üéØ Final recommendation for you:
